---
import heroImg from "../assets/hero.webp";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#fffdf7] text-[#101820]">
	<div class="absolute inset-0 soft-grid opacity-70"></div>
	<div class="relative mx-auto grid w-full max-w-6xl gap-10 px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:items-center lg:px-8 lg:py-16">
		<div class="space-y-7">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/70 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#116b4c] shadow-sm">
				<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#28e08f]"></span>
				<span>Précommande par vagues</span>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<h1 class="max-w-4xl text-4xl font-black leading-[0.95] tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
					Réserve ton stock avant tout le monde.
				</h1>
				<p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-600 sm:text-lg">
					Les commandes sont regroupées, les goûts sont sécurisés, les prix restent propres. Tu choisis, on centralise, tu récupères sans courir après le stock.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-4">
				<a href="/register" class="btn-primary px-5 py-3 text-base">
					<span>Créer un compte</span>
					<span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/precommande" class="btn-secondary px-5 py-3 text-base">Commander maintenant</a>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 pt-2">
				<div class="border-l border-black/10 pl-4">
					<p class="text-2xl font-black">85€</p>
					<p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">par carton</p>
				</div>
				<div class="border-l border-black/10 pl-4">
					<p class="text-2xl font-black">10</p>
					<p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">goûts max</p>
				</div>
				<div class="border-l border-black/10 pl-4">
					<p class="text-2xl font-black">24/7</p>
					<p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">suivi en ligne</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="relative">
			<div class="absolute -right-4 -top-4 z-10 rounded-full bg-[#28e08f] px-4 py-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#101820] shadow-xl">
				Stock réservé
			</div>
			<div class="panel interactive overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] p-3">
				<img src={heroImg.src} alt="Précommande sur mobile" class="aspect-[4/5] w-full rounded-[1.4rem] object-cover" loading="lazy" />
				<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 p-3">
					<div class="rounded-2xl bg-[#101820] p-4 text-white">
						<p class="text-xs font-bold text-white/55">Statut</p>
						<p class="mt-1 text-lg font-black">Ouvert</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-2xl bg-[#28e08f] p-4 text-[#101820]">
						<p class="text-xs font-bold text-[#116b4c]">Livraison</p>
						<p class="mt-1 text-lg font-black">Estimée</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
